  "texts": [
    "Comparison on the prompt engineeringBased on the data presented in Figure 4d, restricting the domain before posing questions can significantly enhance the accuracy of the AI model.",
    "Furthermore, we can examine the differences between various domains and evaluate the significance of providing explanations, as shown in Figure 6.",
    "The technique of prompt engineering reveals improved answer performance after an explanation.",
    "For GPT-3.5, we can conclude that the prompt covering all domains has a higher likelihood of yielding optimal results.",
    "Regarding GPT-4, a more specific domain typically leads to a higher accuracy, but the improvement is not as substantial as with GPT-3.5."
  ]
}